select sch_service_bookings.status as status,
count(*) as serviceCount from `sch_service_bookings` inner join `cmn_customers` on `sch_service_bookings`.`cmn_customer_id` = `cmn_customers`.`id` where `cmn_customers`.`user_id` = 40 group by `sch_service_bookings`.`status`
select `id`, `name`, `site_menu_id`, `route`, `order` from `site_menus` where `status` = 1 order by `order` asc
select `id`, `name` from `cmn_languages` order by default_language desc
select `lang_value` from `cmn_translations` where `cmn_language_id` = 2 and `lang_key` = 'Nueva Cita' limit 1
select `id`, `name`, `site_menu_id`, `route`, `order` from `site_menus` where `status` = 1 order by `order` asc
